 when you need to change the air filter. This thermostat works on two stages of both heating and cooling. That means it will work with almost any HVAC system.","Getting help with any Hunter product isn&#39;t a problem. The website offers instructions for installing and programming any thermostat as well as in-depth FAQs. There is even an online support forum for Hunter product users. This thermostat also comes with a one-year warranty."]},"id":"be112ec9-c81f-4aa7-b42c-1787842dc50a","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"d76980a6-77a0-4165-8883-567ff9e15adc","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["While the Hunter Programmable Max may not be equipped with all the bells and whistles of higher ranked thermostats, this thermostat still provides you with enough features, such as seven-day programming and multi-stage heating and cooling, to help you save energy and money throughout the year."]},"id":"0f37e42a-b431-4647-a53a-f6a9c030755b","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_54842","url":"/hunter-max-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"john-carlsen","url":"/author/john-carlsen","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"John Carlsen","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"jN6fuw55cS2xYQi25mfgkg","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2012-06-21T12:54:48Z","datePublished":"2012-06-21T12:54:48Z","name":"Hunter MAX","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.","review":{"rating":64,"verdict":"The Programmable Max is fine for anyone who is looking for a simple thermostat with easy programming.","pros":["The Energy Guide estimates your savings in real time as you program the thermostat."],"cons":["This thermostat does not have a touchscreen. "]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This pr